ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Sex of subject at birth
Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: Is there garbage, litter, or broken glass in the street or road, on the sidewalks, or in the yard?
Notes: 1= Almost none ; 2= Yes, but not a lot ; 3= Yes quite a bit ; 4= Yes, almost everywhere ; -2=Not Observed; -99= N/A ; 77= Refused ; 88= Missing

ElementDescription: How would you rate the general condition of most of the buildings on the block or within 100 yards of the respondent's home?
Notes: 1= Well-kept with exterior surface in good repair ; 2= Fair condition ; 3= Poor condition with peeling paint and need of repair ; 4= Badly deteriorated ;-2= Not observed ; -99= N/A ; 77= Refused ; 88= Missing

ElementDescription: Is there graffiti on the buildings or walls of the buildings on the block or within 100 yards of the respondent's home?
Notes: 1= None ; 2= Yes, but not a lot ; 3= Yes, quite a bit ; 4= Yes, almost everywhere ; -2, -2 2 Not Observed ; -99= N/A ; 77= Refused ; 88= Missing

ElementDescription: Are there vacant, abandoned, or boarded-up buildings, on the block or within 100 yards of the respondent's home?
Notes: 1= No ; 2= Yes 1 building fits this description ; 3= Yes 2-3 buildings fit this description ; 4= Yes= or  more buildings fit this description ;-2= Not Observed ; -99= N/A ; 77= Refused ; 88= Missing

ElementDescription: Are there abandoned vehicles on the block or within 100 yards of the respondent's home?
Notes: 1= No ; 2= Only one ; 3= 2-3 ; 4= 4 or more ;-2= Not observed ; -99= N/A ; 77= Refused ; 88= Missing
